	<h1 class="title">日本经济不景气，所以“猫咪经济学”就火起来了吗？</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/img/missing_face.png" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">邵泓惠 </span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2016-02-23 19:00:45 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/22735/medium/22735.jpg?1456217924" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


<div class="com-share" data-id="22735" data-title="《日本经济不景气，所以“猫咪经济学”就火起来了吗？》，来自@好奇心日报" data-pic="http://www.qdaily.com/system/articles/articleshows/22735/medium/22735.jpg?1456217924" data-url="http://www.qdaily.com/mobile/articles/22735.html" data-weiboAppkey="2462590045">
